author: The Critical Drinker
description: Both Wicked and Gladiator 2 have opened strong this weekend. Meanwhile, Disney still haven't released the Snow White trailer online, and Captain America 4 has been delayed for even more reshoots. Join me, MauLer, Disparu, Tyrone Magnus and Box Office Brawler at the Bar!
title: Open Bar #120 - Glicked Dominates, Snow White Panic, Captain America Disaster
